TITLE: Configuring Backend Actions in CopilotRuntime with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to define a backend action in CopilotKit that allows the AI to fetch user data. It creates a CopilotRuntime instance with an action named 'fetchNameForUserId' that simulates retrieving a user's name from a database based on their ID.
