TITLE: Adding Custom CopilotKit Config to Search Node
DESCRIPTION: Modification of the search_node function to include a custom CopilotKit configuration. This config describes the intermediate state that will be emitted during the search process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/copilotkit/copilotkit/blob/main/docs/content/docs/coagents/tutorials/ai-travel-app/step-5-stream-progress.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
