TITLE: Implementing LangChain Adapter with OpenAI Integration
DESCRIPTION: Creates a LangChain adapter function that initializes ChatOpenAI model with GPT-4, configures tools, and sets up streaming with conversation tracking metadata.
SOURCE: https://github.com/copilotkit/copilotkit/blob/main/docs/content/docs/(root)/(other)/observability/langsmith.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const { LangChainAdapter } = await import("@copilotkit/runtime");
const { ChatOpenAI } = await import("@langchain/openai");

async function getLangChainOpenAIAdapter() {
  return new LangChainAdapter({
    chainFn: async ({ messages, tools, threadId }) => {
      const model = new ChatOpenAI({
        modelName: "gpt-4-1106-preview",
      }).bindTools(tools, {
        strict: true,
      });
      return model.stream(messages, {
        tools,
        metadata: { conversation_id: threadId },
      });
    },
  });
}
```

